text:
Hej <@UBJBQE4NB> Jep, the latest Quartierspiegel come from 2015 (see Link below). Actually, we are about to transform all data from the Statistical Yearbooks into Linked Data and this data will be available at TWIST. The Data from the Quartierspiegel are not completely available until then, but will follow a bit later.  

<https://www.stadt-zuerich.ch/prd/de/index/statistik/publikationen-angebote/publikationen.html?ob=jcr%3Acontent%2F%40publicationDate&om=desc&sfExtended=false&q=quartierspiegel&q_tg=&q_type=publicationstatistik#resultStart>

Also the data that is contained in ZüriZahlen-App will be in Linked Data. Currently we have this as Open Data, but it's not a DB that's accessible: <https://data.stadt-zuerich.ch/dataset/daten-zur-zuerizahlen-app>

attachments.title: Daten zur ZüriZahlen App - CKAN
attachments.text: Dieser Datensatz gibt dem interessierten Entwickler die Möglichkeit, auf Datensätze aus der ZüriZahlen App zuzugreifen.

Current Open Data based on Stadtquartiere: <https://data.stadt-zuerich.ch/dataset?q=stadtquartier&page=1>
